note over browser:
the eventhandler of submit button
in js file creates a new note with 
input data, adds it to the notes 
list and renders notes list on page
end note 

note over browser:
browser sends the new note as 
JSON-data to server via 
POST-request
end note 

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa

